snippet.title: SkidStorm Alpha Trailer
snippet.description:
We want to collect user feedback and statistics before the global launch. For this, we are inviting you to try the game before everyone else.

Download link: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.immobilegames.skidstorm

Features: 
• Synchronous multiplayer
• Rank based matchmaking & custom lobby system
• 11 upgradeable cars
• Single player mode with a tough AI
• Time trial mode, player ghosts & leaderboards
